ActIndian Act
SubjectProgram and Service Expenditures O-Pipon-Na-Piwi Cree Nation
PrecisOrder extending the authority of the Minister of Indigenous Services to make program and service expenditures for the O-Pipon-Na-Piwin Cree Nation at South Indian Lake, as if that community was on reserve lands, until the earlier of the date that the lands at South Indian Lake are set apart as reserve lands or March 31, 2033.
